NBA AWARDS SHOW
June 24, 2019
Luka Doncic
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 
 Q.  So out there you seemed pretty at ease.  Did you have any apprehension about tonight?  
LUKA DONCIC: I mean, I always feel confident, but, like I said, Deandre [Ayton] and Trae [Young] had amazing seasons so I wasn't that confident.  But, I'm happy to have it and it's, like I said, special.   
 Q.  Luka, congratulations.  Is there anyone you would like to single out who helped you during your first season in doing so well?  
LUKA DONCIC: I mean, there was like so many persons to help me.  First of all, my family, of course, and my teammates and coaches and everybody behind that, you know, there has been just a lot of players, a lot of people that helped me.   
  
  
  
  
  

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT